{{! Tenant write-lock / grace banner (design section 8.2, ruling 9).
Locked: writes blocked server-side, reads and export stay. Lifted: grace
until the lift date, then the lock re-applies automatically. }}
{{#if @lockState.locked}}
  <div
    class="alert alert-error tenant-lock-banner"
    data-test-tenant-lock-banner
  >
    <Ui::Ph @icon="lock" @size="18px" />
    <span>You are over your limits. Reduce or pay to continue. Your data is safe
      and stays readable and exportable.</span>
  </div>
{{else if @lockState.lifted}}
  <div
    class="alert alert-warning tenant-lock-banner"
    data-test-tenant-grace-banner
  >
    <Ui::Ph @icon="clock" @size="18px" />
    <span>Your account is active until
      {{format-date @lockState.liftUntil}}. Settle before then to keep access.</span>
  </div>
{{/if}}